    dc:description "FIGURE 7. Chrysis rasmonti Rosa, sp. nov., ♂, holotype. A) Habitus, dorsal view. B) Head, frontal view. C) Genital capsule. D) Metasoma, postero-lateral view. E) Habitus, lateral view. F) Metasoma, ventral view. Scale bars 1.0 mm." ;
