    dc:description "FIGURE 9. Chrysis verna Dahlbom, 1854. A–D, ♀, from Greece: Pyrgos (Linsenmaier collection). A) Habitus, dorsal view. B) Mesosoma, lateral view. C) Metasoma, postero-lateral view. D) Metasoma, ventral view. Chrysis samia Bischoff, 1910. E–G, ♀, holotype. E) Mesosoma, dorsal view. F) Metasoma, lateral view. G) Head, frontal view. Scale bars 1.0 mm." ;
